{"type": "article", "id": 11788, "title": "自行车挂架", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-08T11:30:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141158uiSVWAPFrKbTYeGM.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个看起来像是小挂钩的产品是瑞典设计师 Karl Mikael Ling 带来的一款自行车挂架，名字叫做“Pincher”，它采用纯白色的外形，看上去简单轻巧，但能够承受 30 公斤的重量，经过测试，悬挂在砖墙，混凝土，木墙上都可以，把自行车挂在墙上，既能够节省空间，看起来又酷酷的。这款产品售价 80 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.karlmikaelling.com/store/pincher\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135828IqkrfRcutgAMTDFh.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261358299LZAIohyPjXVH4kr.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135829PrzyiYlunHgb6X2S.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}